val df1 = spark.read.format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra").options(Map( "table" -> "articles_and_events", "keyspace" -> "queries" )).load().registerTempTable("query_1")


var SQLDate = z.select("SQLDate", list("query_1", "date")).asInstanceOf[String]
var Language = z.select("Language", list("query_1", "language")).asInstanceOf[String]
var Country = z.select("Country", list("query_1", "country")).asInstanceOf[String]
var query = " SELECT date, language, country, count(DISTINCT documentid) as number_article,  count(DISTINCT eventid) as number_event FROM query_1 WHERE date == '" +  SQLDate + "'  AND language = '" +  Language + "' AND country = '" +  Country + "' GROUP BY date, language, country"
var df1 = sqlContext.sql(query)
println("%table " + df1.columns.mkString("\t"))
println(df1.map(x => x.mkString("\t")).collect().mkString("\n"))

val df3 = spark.read.format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra").options(Map( "table" -> "controversial_actors", "keyspace" -> "queries" )).load().registerTempTable("query_3")

val SQLDate = z.select("Month", list("query_3", "eventmonth")).asInstanceOf[String]
val Language = z.select("Language", list("query_3", "language")).asInstanceOf[String]
val Country = z.select("Country", list("query_3", "countryname")).asInstanceOf[String]
val PosNeg = z.select("Neg / Pos", Array(("positive","positive"), ("negative","negative"))).asInstanceOf[String]
val query = "select actorcode, actorname, sum(abs(" +  PosNeg + ")) as " +  PosNeg + "  from query_3 where eventmonth== '" +  SQLDate + "' and  language== '" +  Language + "' and  countryname== '" +  Country + "' group by actorcode, actorname  order by " +  PosNeg + " desc"
val df3 = sqlContext.sql(query)
println("%table " + df3.columns.mkString("\t"))
println(df3.map(x => x.mkString("\t")).collect().mkString("\n"))

val df4 = spark.read.format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra").options(Map( "table" -> "divided_actors", "keyspace" -> "queries" )).load().registerTempTable("query_4")

var SQLDate = z.select("Date", list("query_4", "eventdate")).asInstanceOf[String]
var query = "SELECT actor, (SUM(variance * nb_article) / SUM(nb_article)) AS mean FROM query_4 WHERE eventdate == '" +  SQLDate + "'  GROUP BY actor ORDER BY mean DESC"
var df4 = sqlContext.sql(query)
println("%table " + df4.columns.mkString("\t"))
println(df4.map(x => x.mkString("\t")).collect().mkString("\n"))

val df51 = spark.read.format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra").options(Map( "table" -> "tone_actors_daily", "keyspace" -> "queries" )).load().registerTempTable("query_5_1")

var actor2 = z.select("Actor 2", list("query_5_1", "Actor2Name")).asInstanceOf[String]
var query = "SELECT date, daily_avg_tone  FROM query_5_1 WHERE actor1name = '" +  actor1 + "'  AND actor2name = '" + actor2 +"'"
